AB  - Smart flexible microfluidic technology (SFMT) innovatively integrates microfluidic technology, Flexible sensor and artificial intelligence (AI). Precise manipulation of microfluidic samples by microfluidic technology, flexible sensing highly attuned to biological interfaces, and real-time analysis of dynamic data and intelligent decision-making by AI help to improve detection sensitivity and adaptability to complex environments, and provide noninvasive continuous detection of health, which makes smart health management possible. Starting from intelligent sensors manufacturing, this paper elaborates on the types of microfluidic chips, detection mechanisms, and multimodal AI decision-making. The materials, structures, processing methods of microfluidic chips manufacturing and the characteristics of AI enhanced microfluidic chips are analyzed in depth. Emerging applications of SFMT in diverse fields such as human healthcare, pet health, and farm animals are comprehensively summarized. In addition, we analyze the strengths and weaknesses of SFMT and provide insights into its development prospects. In the future, SFMT will make great strides toward precise sensing, AI and diversification, which will help SFMT gradually transform from a theoretical concept to a wide range of efficient and practical applications for a healthier life with a higher happiness index.
