TI  - Multimodal metabolic and functional network signatures for diagnosis of parkinson's disease: a PET/MR study
T2  - SCIENTIFIC REPORTS
LA  - English
KW  - PET/MR
KW  - JSSE
KW  - Metabolic brain network
